description: The masculine and ripped Trent Diesel is back again. This week he takes on newcomer, Ryan Rockford. Ryan is an ex navy seal who has training in judo, boxing, and wrestling. His body is solid muscle. In order to improve his skills, Trent has been hitting the gym and doing lots of cardio, combined with explosion sets. He plans to let his opponent wear himself out till the point of exhaustion and then slam him into the mat. In preparation for his first match, Ryan has been working hard on his endurance, along with some high intensity weight training. He is confident he will be able to out strategize and out power Trent with no problems. They are both looking forward to fucking the hell out of the other stud, but someone always has to submit. Who will it be this week?
title: Trent Diesel vs Ryan Rockford
